item.title: SoftLayer_Metric_Tracking_Object_Type
item.description: SoftLayer_Metric_Tracking_Object_Type Datatype Description SoftLayer [[SoftLayer_Metric_Tracking_Object|tracking objects]] can model various kinds of measured data, from server and virtual server bandwidth usage to CPU use to remote storage usage. SoftLayer_Metric_Tracking_Object_Type models one of these types and is referred to in tracking objects to reflect what type of data they track. Local keyname Description A tracking object type's key name. This is a shorter description of what kind of data a tracking object group is polling.
